  "page": "Wood dancers",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> This article or section is a <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stub\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Stub\">stub</a>. You can help \"A Wiki Of Ice And Fire\" by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Wood_dancers&amp;action=edit\">expanding it</a> and/or improving existing text.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Wood dancers</b> were the hunters among the <a href=\"/index.php/Children_of_the_forest\" title=\"Children of the forest\">children of the forest</a>. During the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_First_Men_and_the_children_of_the_forest\" title=\"War of the First Men and the children of the forest\">war of the First Men and the children of the forest</a>, wood dancers became warriors, but despite their secret arts of tree and leaf, they could only slow the advance of the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_the_coming_of_the_first_men.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_the_coming_of_the_first_men.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wood_dancers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_the_coming_of_the_first_men.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_the_coming_of_the_first_men.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Ancient History: The Coming of the First Men.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404163651\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.012 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.014 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 135/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8821/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1777/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 467/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 721/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    7.214      1 -total\n 55.68%    4.017      1 Template:Ref\n 34.86%    2.515      1 Template:Ref/core\n 23.18%    1.672      1 Template:Stub\n 19.38%    1.398      1 Template:References\n 14.71%    1.061      1 Template:Mbox\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:23092-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404163651 and revision id 192980\n -->\n",
